msgid "Visual SLAM"
msgstr "Visual SLAM"

msgid ""
"Visual SLAM is TriOrb BASE's map building and self-localization engine based"
" on stereo keyframe features. Its internal wrapper API is considered "
"implementation detail and is not covered in this reference."
msgstr ""
"Visual SLAM は、ステレオキーフレーム特徴量にもとづく TriOrb BASE の地図生成・自己位置推定エンジンです。内部ラッパーの API "
"は実装詳細として扱い、本リファレンスでは公開していません。"

msgid "Role on TriOrb BASE"
msgstr "TriOrb BASE における役割"

msgid "Responsibility"
msgstr "役割"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "説明"

msgid "Map building"
msgstr "地図生成"

msgid ""
"Builds a 3D keyframe-based map while the robot is driven through the "
"environment"
msgstr "手動走行やリモコン走行中にステレオ特徴量から 3D キーフレーム地図を構築"

msgid "Self-localization"
msgstr "自己位置推定"

msgid ""
"Estimates 6-DoF robot pose at runtime by matching stereo features against "
"the stored map"
msgstr "保存済み地図とステレオ特徴量を照合して実行時に 6 自由度のロボット姿勢を推定"

msgid "Map export"
msgstr "地図エクスポート"

msgid ""
"Exports the 3D map to a 2D occupancy representation used by downstream "
"navigation"
msgstr "ナビゲーションが利用する 2D 占有格子表現に 3D 地図を変換"

msgid "Map I/O"
msgstr "地図 I/O"

msgid "Saves / loads map files to the robot controller and PC"
msgstr "ロボットコントローラや PC との間で地図ファイルの保存・読み込みを実施"

msgid "API"
msgstr "API"

msgid ""
"Visual SLAM itself does not expose a public ROS 2 API. Day-to-day "
"interaction is through higher-level packages that consume its output:"
msgstr "Visual SLAM 自体は公開 ROS 2 API を提供しません。運用では出力を利用する以下の上位パッケージを経由します:"

msgid "Package"
msgstr "パッケージ"

msgid "Role"
msgstr "役割"

msgid "[`triorb_vslam_tf`](triorb_vslam_tf/index.md)"
msgstr "[`triorb_vslam_tf`](triorb_vslam_tf/index.md)"

msgid "Publishes VSLAM-derived pose as TF."
msgstr "VSLAM 由来の姿勢を TF として配信。"

msgid "[`trirob_vslam_tf_bridge`](trirob_vslam_tf_bridge/index.md)"
msgstr "[`trirob_vslam_tf_bridge`](trirob_vslam_tf_bridge/index.md)"

msgid "Bridges VSLAM to navigation pose."
msgstr "VSLAM 姿勢をナビゲーション用姿勢へブリッジ。"

msgid "[`triorb_dead_reckoning`](triorb_dead_reckoning/index.md)"
msgstr "[`triorb_dead_reckoning`](triorb_dead_reckoning/index.md)"

msgid "Fuses VSLAM, odometry, and IMU for robust pose."
msgstr "VSLAM・オドメトリ・IMU を統合し堅牢な自己位置を推定。"

msgid "[REST API](https://triorb-inc.github.io/TriOrb-AMR-Robot-Controller/)"
msgstr "[REST API](https://triorb-inc.github.io/TriOrb-AMR-Robot-Controller/)"

msgid "Map save / load / switch operations over HTTP."
msgstr "地図保存・読み込み・切替操作（HTTP）。"

msgid ""
"See each package's API page for its public topics, services, and actions."
msgstr "公開されているトピック / サービス / アクションは各パッケージの API ページを参照してください。"

